abstract: The Algeria A' national football team (Arabic: منتخب الجزائر لكرة القدم للمحليين ‎) is the local national football team of Algeria and is open only to domestic league players. The team represents Algeria at the African Nations Championship and is controlled by the Algerian Football Federation.

The Algeria A' national football team (Arabic: منتخب الجزائر لكرة القدم للمحليين ‎) is the local national football team of Algeria and is open only to domestic league players. The team represents Algeria at the African Nations Championship and is controlled by the Algerian Football Federation.
L'Équipe d'Algérie de football A' représente l'Algérie dans les compétitions de football contenant des joueurs locaux comme le Championnat d'Afrique des nations.
منتخب الجزائر لكرة القدم للمحليين هو منتخب لكرة القدم للاعبي البطولة الوطنية الجزائرية.
